Because this file uses proportional spacing, it is meant to be
printed on the Xerox 9700 printer in Forysthe Hall rather than read
online.  To print the document, type the PRINT 1/LAST command.
OPTIONS: UNN CC NOEJECT TRC PFORMAT=SYSZ10 FORMS=3HOL DUPLEX FCB=FULL
